                    "value": "<p>Zini makes fun of either Aezar or Grizzle while she can observe them within 30 feet of her. She attempts a @Check[deception|against:will] check with a +2 circumstance bonus against the creature's Will DC. Zini cannot use this ability again against that creature until she spends at least 10 minutes thinking about a worthy second insult.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> As success, but the target also takes @Damage[(1d4+2)[mental]] damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Off-Guard] against the next attack an ally attempts against the target before the beginning of Zini's next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>"
